name: ElasticExport
description: This is the elastic export plugin for plentymarkets 7. The elastic export is used to create export formats for price search engines, price comparison portals, markets and affiliate service providers.
author: plentymarkets GmbH
license: GNU AFFERO GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE Version 3, 19 November 2007

shortDescription.de: Dies ist das Plugin ElasticExport für plentymarkets 7. Der elastische Export wird verwendet, um Exportformate für Preissuchmaschinen, Preisvergleichsportale, Marktplätze und Affiliateserviceanbieter zu erstellen.
shortDescription.en: This is the ElasticExport plugin for plentymarkets 7. The elastic export is used to create export formats for price search engines, price comparison portals, markets and affiliate service providers.
